title: Last Show of the Season
description:
Jason Fitz, Trevor Matich, and Greg McElroy talk about the lessons learned from an unprecedent 2020 season and what the CFB can learn moving forward. They discuss college stars playing in the Super Bowl this weekend and make their bold predictions for next year.
